xxl.core.xml.relational
Class StringToSQLTypeConverterMap

java.lang.Object
  xxl.core.xml.relational.StringToSQLTypeConverterMap

public class StringToSQLTypeConverterMap
extends Object

This class consists of a map which maps SQL-Types to StringToSQLTypeConverters.

The method getObject(String S, String SQLTypeName) tries to convert a string into a java-object with the specified SQLType.
The following table shows the default mapping for various common SQL data types.

SQL type Java type
CHAR String
VARCHAR String
LONGVARCHAR String
NUMERIC java.math.BigDecimal
DECIMAL java.math.BigDecimal
BIT Boolean
TINYINT Byte
SMALLINT Short
INTEGER Integer
BIGINT Long
REAL Float
FLOAT Double
DOUBLE Double
BINARY byte[]
VARBINARY byte[]
LONGVARBINARY byte[]
DATE java.sql.Date
TIME java.sql.Time
TIMESTAMP java.sql.Timestamp
COUNTER java.lang.Integer
